  </p>

  <p>
    Project inquiries run through
    <a href="https://rosenthaler.co">rosenthaler.co</a> &mdash; everything else, just email me.
  </p>

  <ul class="links">
    <li><a href="mailto:maximilian@gravemeyer.com">maximilian@gravemeyer.com</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mgravemeyer/" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://github.com/mgravemeyer" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
